metadata.name: SAKURA MEGAMI
metadata.description:
Fan art for the MEGAMI project. #megamiathome

One of the words in the language of cherry blossoms is "a graceful woman," and I have drawn a woman who fits the name MEGAMI.

Naoki Saito SENSEI's thoughts on the MEGAMI project, which he also talked about in his video, are wonderful, and I agree with them.

This work complies with the MEGAMI Art License.
